# Warp Anchor Systems Overview (2025-06-04)

## Core Concepts
- Warp anchors/zones are Universal Magic manifestations, not just tech
- Anchor creation/restoration is skill-gated by Universal Language puzzles
- Anchors are tradable, discoverable, and multiplayer-enabled (quantum bookmarks)
- Anchor use interacts with the Timestream Framework, causing timeline branches and narrative consequences

## Technical
- Robust serialization, hashing, and validation for anchor data
- Configurable visual/audio effects for anchor actions
- Automated tests for edge cases, multiplayer, and anchor sharing
- Accessibility options for all anchor effects

## UI/UX
- Intuitive anchor management panel with puzzle integration
- Minimap/world overlays for anchor locations and status
- Tutorials, tooltips, and feedback for anchor actions
